<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạ̉ywh wʿdtk bs qsyt lḥẓạt ḍʿfy kẖdtny bʿyd
 hnt ʿly wsbt ạ̹ydyk bs bʿyd ạ̉nạ bạbqy̱ wḥyd
 ạlqrạr- nfsy ạ̹rạdty tkwn gẖlbạny wạ̉qdr ạ̉ʿysẖ fy rḍạk mrtạḥ
 ạ̉nsy̱ ạlkẖwf wsạʿạt ạlḥyrẗ tlms ḍʿfy thdy ryạḥ
 2- sẖạyf lmʿẗ ʿyny wʿạrf ạ̹nk sạkn rwḥy wqlby
 wkfwfy ạlmftwḥẗ btṭlb rby btʿln lyk ʿn ḥby
 3- ʿmry mạ fkrt ạ̉jrḥ fyk bạḍʿf lkn mn gẖyr qṣd
 ḥbk jwh ḍlwʿy byjry wlạ bạrtạḥ ạ̉bdaⁿạ fy ạlbʿd</lyrics>
<title>wʿdtk</title>
</song>